### App health
GET http://localhost:8080/api/training/health

### GPU info
GET http://localhost:8080/api/gpu/info

### GPU health
GET http://localhost:8080/api/gpu/health

### Start training
POST http://localhost:8080/api/training/start

### Check training status
GET http://localhost:8080/api/training/status

### Run backend benchmark (returns fallback-java if direct backend op is unsupported)
POST http://localhost:8080/api/gpu/benchmark

### (Optional) Switch backend manually, then restart app
POST http://localhost:8080/api/gpu/switch?backend=CPU
Content-Type: application/x-www-form-urlencoded

